beer.beer_description: A modern punchy California-style IPA, brewed for the iconic Carwyn Cellars Canvent. We've started with a super clean Pilsner base, then hit it with a heavy dry-hop of Eclipse, Citra, Mosaic, & Citra Hyperboost. We're getting waves of tropical and citrus fruits, finishing with dry, crispy finish.
